        "subject": "LU-874 ptlrpc: handle in-flight hqreq correctly",
        "message": "LU-874 ptlrpc: handle in-flight hqreq correctly\n\n--- debug use only ---\nIf there are in-flight requests pending, we shouldn't timeout the\ncorresponding ldlm locks. We shouldn't remove the requests from export\nexp_queued_rpc list until the requests are really finished.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Idd516a8ae3f88574469b13d0d03debb81640ee7b\n"
      },
